textContent:
4-6 Dashes Angostura Bitters
2 Dashes Absinthe 
1 Barspoon Grenadine
1 Barspoon Falernum
1 Barspoon Cinnamon Syrup
.75 oz  Column Still Aged Rum 
.75 oz  Blended Aged Rum 
.5 oz  Black Blended Overproof Rum 

Build in a rocks glass
Garnish with a Peel of Grapefruit & Lime, and grate Cinnamon
